						               													<description>This 'ORIGINAL EDITION' is named so because its the first of the Question card format games, following the previous 'COUPLES INTIMACY EDITION' board game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this ORIGINAL EDITION, questions are ranked A, B or C depending on whether you want a quick lite game (A's) or deeper questions (C's) or play A,B,C in order.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Player one asks the selected question of the other player(s), and they answer with the total Truth, or a total Lie. Player one has to guess is it Truth or a Lie and gains a point if they identified it correctly. This can also be played as a drinking game where the wrong guess means you take a drink. Suitable for 2-8 players 16+y/o for normal games and older if its a drinking game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game can also be played co-cooperatively, where all questions are Truth and take turns to ask the other(s). Lose a point for no answer given or you want to skip. Alternatively focus more on the answers and interesting conversations normally ensue for clarification or shared experiences together.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
